Column Description: The Type of Requester which initiated the process

Name: payment_arrangement_id
Column Description: The Unique Identifier of the Payment Arrangement related to this event

Name: owner_customer_id
Column Description: Business contact id of the owner of agreement, could be a natural person, a complex or another legal entity

Name: holder_customer_id
Column Description: Business contact id of the holder of the instrume, only natural persons allowed.

Name: previous_owner_customer_id
Column Description: Business contact id of the owner of agreement after change , could be a natural person, a complex or another legal entity

Name: previous_holder_customer_id
Column Description: Business contact id of the holder of the instrument after change, only natural persons allowed.

Name: clearing_account_id
Column Description: Unique Identifier of account that will be debitted or credited during transactions. Accounts could swap in the future.

Name: previous_clearing_account_id
Column Description: Unique Identifier of account that was used as a clearing account before it changed

Name: initial_account_id
Column Description: Unique Identifier of account that will be used for payment of the product, as well as the iban that will be printed on the next cards. Might change in future.

Name: printed_iban
Column Description: The IBAN that is printed on the card

Column Description: The Id of the Requester which initaited the process

Name: card_sequence_number
Column Description: The three digit number on the card.

Name: printed_name_line_1
Column Description: First name line on the card, should be the name of the customer in most cases

Name: printed_name_line_2
Column Description: Second name line on the card, could hold the holder of the card. In most cases empty
